2001-01-22  Darin Adler  <darin@eazel.com>

	* gnome-vfs-mime-magic:
	* gnome-vfs.applications:
	* gnome-vfs.keys.in:
	* gnome-vfs.mime:
	Got rid of minor whitespace anomalies -- always use tabs to
	indent, don't put any tab on blank lines, no trailing
	whitespace allowed.

